## Token Pipeline

### Flow

```
tokens/*.json  (source of truth)
    ↓  scripts/generate-css-tokens.js
src/styles/tokens/tokens-*.css  (generated)
    ↓  scripts/generate-tailwind-preset.js
tailwind.preset.js  (generated)
```

### Rules

1. Edit `tokens/dark.json` and `tokens/light.json` — never edit generated CSS or preset files directly.
2. After editing token sources, regenerate outputs via the scripts.
3. When adding a new semantic token, add it to both `dark.json` and `light.json`.
4. `generate-custom-tokens.js` and `generate-token-docs.js` are supplementary scripts — run them when the task involves custom tokens or documentation.

### Verification

```bash
node tokens/generate-css-tokens.js
node tokens/generate-tailwind-preset.js
pnpm build
```
